  "texts": [
    "The complete API call, along with the exact prompt, the temperature, and other hyper-parameters are included in S3 Table.",
    "The prompt included a request to return these results in a JSON format.",
    "ChatGPT's response (full), as well as the JSON formatted dialogue response were recorded in one session on June 9th 2023.",
    "The notes sent to ChatGPT were text-only, stripped of the rich-text formatting (RTF) native to our EHR system (Epic Systems, Verona, WI).",
    "This reduced token count by approximately ten-fold, enabling notes to fit into the GPT4-8K input window and removing a substantial source of confusion for the LLM in prompt tuning."
